{"tid":1791584,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"邊個再照單全收狗講個套，幫手足認有軍火，邊個就係鬼","createTime":"2019-12-21T03:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T09:31:31.000Z","uid":33904,"like":105,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"54eacb3e141f31f230e28b86be8424cd6b6dc762","tid":1791584,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"你班友到底係弱智定鬼？<br />\n次次一有咩炸彈、軍火，就撲出黎認哂去，<br />\n屈鳩懷疑狗插贓嫁禍既人割席？<br />\n<br />\n我屌你<br />\n第一，狗講咩你信咩？唔洗自己思考？唔洗自己確認？幾時變到咁聽狗話？<br />\n<br />\n第二，就算d軍火真係自己友既，你地認黎有撚用？緊係搵疑點幫手足打甩。證明d軍火係手足做責任係d狗度，我地要做既野一定係幫手足甩身。<br />\n<br />\n講埋d乜鳩香港人接受唔到有槍？<br />\n核爆都唔割係得把口？<br />\n<br />\n你班弱智，<br />\n人都比人拉左，<br />\n你地可唔可以醒少少？<br />\n<br />\n割席係講緊唔承認呢個人係我地既人，<br />\n亦唔提供任何協助，甚至落井下石。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幾時連懷疑d狗都變成割席？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a54707067bcebe6ebc780ce48595d82bef598a4d","tid":1791584,"uid":144,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:31:40.000Z","msg":"一開始又話打劫找換店<br />\n2點鐘又改口話有合理理由懷疑示威用途<br />\n睇到我頭都大撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e58e2d2c583501e2f6dd44a00ec3aabd7b9ae1","tid":1791584,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b25a686af72d01c8eaa3ffea99f2bfcc722c21de","tid":1791584,"uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"熱青城咁多人上水幫人認左佢都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b56bd56b7ea6efebf118be15e99a16a28a79fa","tid":1791584,"uid":158888,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"仲有個証人話見到狗捉住個男仔先<br />\n咁樣懷疑吓成件事都好合理掛<br />\n咁都要俾人話割"},{"pid":"1b6a6d2a1b317722819c013f038f24b8c5785a68","tid":1791584,"uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"明明比人屈 個個衝出黎認 然後話不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人屈 同割唔割有咩關係啊"},{"pid":"a9edbf0ff8550f6e53734042afc30b24247a1162","tid":1791584,"uid":258696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔割唔等於爭住認"},{"pid":"917b4662b515b676745e1b110e355462df6e0b53","tid":1791584,"uid":21279,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b25a686af72d01c8eaa3ffea99f2bfcc722c21de","tid":1791584,"uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"熱青城咁多人上水幫人認左佢都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"你係泛民含撚派<br />\n一定係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfc957fc287f18f7af34ffaa480b7327ff09b6c","tid":1791584,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1b6a6d2a1b317722819c013f038f24b8c5785a68","tid":1791584,"uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"明明比人屈 個個衝出黎認 然後話不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比人屈 同割唔割有咩關係啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"從來我地連登冇人會割 但總有班on9衝出黎 見你一有質疑 就話係你想割"},{"pid":"51dddce77dc8a1f6e01567cd796864e4d10d59a4","tid":1791584,"uid":33904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我而家先知唔割席即係唔好幫手足搵疑點，信哂狗講個套！</span><br />\n<br />\n真係唔知咩野先叫割席！<br />\n<br />\n唔割席係手足中左伏都幫佢兜，<br />\n敵人指控手足，<br />\n要幫手足搵疑點甩身。<br />\n<br />\n你班垃圾淨係諗住點樣推高武力接受程度，<br />\n唔理被捕手足死活，<br />\n輿論打壓試圖調查疑點既人。<br />\n<br />\n從來冇人覺得用槍係鬼，<br />\n我地只係對狗既講法有懷疑，<br />\n怕手足被人屈。"},{"pid":"5ad4fe34e29fffe50b5742e6f9122f107dd53b19","tid":1791584,"uid":3987,"like":1,"d